---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer class="site-footer">
	<div class="footer-shell">
		<p class="footer-title">The 0.5 Chronicles / 《地球文明0.5编年史》</p>
		<p class="footer-copy">
			A people’s history of the transition from the late mechanical age to the AI era.
			<br />
			记录从大机器时代余晖到 AI 时代成形之间的人类过渡现场。
		</p>
		<p class="footer-meta">© {today.getFullYear()} Yang Yu. Built as a living chronicle.</p>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	.site-footer {
		margin-top: 4rem;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(var(--gray), 0.14);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
	}

	.footer-shell {
		width: min(1100px, calc(100% - 2rem));
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.footer-title {
		margin: 0 0 0.45rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: rgb(var(--black));
	}

	.footer-copy,
	.footer-meta {
		margin: 0.35rem 0;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}
</style>
